				<td colspan="2"><span>Bards have very low dps on their own, and aren't really meant for tanking. I'm not that surprised at the results. I'd guess the bard took quite a bit of time and the beastlord killed a lot faster. You might also find beastlord combat tables differ from bard ones.
<br />

<br />
Problem is you're playing to the beastlord's strengths and not the bard's stengths. Try changing the bard tactics, lots of options:
<br />

<br />
1) Charm a mob and stick it on the seafury.
<br />
2) Kite it around using chants
<br />
3) Snare/Fear kite it
<br />

<br />
You can easily then change the tables... bard finishes fight 100% health, beastlord as before. </span></td>
